    "The overview of the spaCy Model is given in Figure 1.",
    "The next step is to implement a system pipeline by using the spaCy model to generate a literature review segment automatically.",
    "The system takes the DOI and PDF files of multiple papers as input.",
    "It uses the Requests library to collect the paper titles and first author names from the DOI.",
    "Then it uses PYPDF2 and Regular Expression (RE) libraries to collect only the conclusion of each PDF."
